    <context>The @spaarke/ui-components library provides 37+ reusable React components shared across PCF controls, Code Pages, and solution pages. It uses Fluent UI v9, supports dark mode theming, and provides PCF-safe exports compatible with React 16. No architecture document captures this component library end-to-end.</context>
