      - Map composition patterns: how components compose with each other
      - Document theming system: Fluent UI v9 tokens, dark mode, custom tokens
      - Explain PCF-safe exports: how React 18 components are made compatible with React 16 PCF hosts
      - Include build pipeline and package structure
      - Cite source files for every component
    </constraints>
  </prompt>
